box\">\n<div class=\"description-title\">January 18 - 18km</div>\n<div>\n2025-01-18 <img src=\"https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1442152045/vector/path-route-icon-distance-symbol.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=2ilIa1pWHJp550B31t__1NPc0CHpouutgdxt7QO4EJg=\" class=\"static-icon\">18 km <img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS_EkMEkMAdgDcE0W6nELzmmMrqHToRcoS8eA&s\" class=\"static-icon\">1133 m <img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.freepik.com/512/13063/13063145.png\" class=\"static-icon\"><span>5:03:44</span>\n        <a href=\"https://www.strava.com/activities/13387118399\" class=\"icon-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/strava-2.svg\" class=\"icon\"></a></div>\n\n<br>\n\n<div class=\"description-text\">Tried out the new snow shoes, huge improvement over trying to scramble up steep slopes in the trail running shoes. Trail 1/52 in 2025.\n\n\u26f0\ufe0f Sebaldstein (1,733 m) \u2022 \u26f0\ufe0f Taubenstein (1,692 m) \u2022 \u26f0\ufe0f Taubensteinsattel (1,580 m) | \ud83c\udf10 summitbag</div>\n\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 100%; height: 220px; aspect-ratio: 3 / 1;\">\n  <iframe src=\"/strava-collections/_static/activity-13387118399.html\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; border:none; border-radius: 12px;\"></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"gallery\"><a href=\"https://d35tn3x5zm6xrc.cloudfront.net/eziu1vxOtZfX6HSy3tnmQ8GByoXbcV01Xo02y5eR00lS2U/thumbnails/zxv5NZFh0eXwYg-YQMbEcfZ-F33vnJTcnwaY7o57Sec_1080x1920.jpg\" class=\"glightbox\" data-gallery=\"collection-gallery-5\"><img src=\"https://d35tn3x5zm6xrc.cloudfront.net/eziu1vxOtZfX6HSy3tnmQ8GByoXbcV01Xo02y5eR00lS2U/thumbnails/zxv5NZFh0eXwYg-YQMbEcfZ-F33vnJTcnwaY7o57Sec_1080x1920.jpg\" height=\"200\" class=\"lightbox-trigger\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"January 18 - 18km photo 1\"></a><a href=\"https://dgtzuqphqg23d.cloudfront.net/MTT6XnXloW6pC9QxpFyvMka1tjNMQEVP6j3OcIb4f2Q-768x576.jpg\" class=\"glightbox\" data-gallery=\"coll